@startuml
title Dietas — Flujo de Autenticacion (actual)

actor "Enfermero/a" as Nurse
participant "App (Expo)" as App
participant "AsyncStorage" as Storage
participant "Mock API (json-server)" as MockAPI

== Inicio de App ==
App -> Storage: hydrate() → getItem('@dietas:auth')
Storage -> App: null o { token, user }

alt Sesion guardada (Recordarme)
  App -> App: Restaura user + token en Zustand
  App -> Nurse: Splash fade-out → Pantalla principal (app)/
else Sin sesion
  App -> Nurse: Splash fade-out → LoginScreen
end

== Login ==
Nurse -> App: Ingresa usuario + password
Nurse -> App: (opcional) Marca "Recordarme"
Nurse -> App: Presiona "Ingresar"

App -> MockAPI: GET /nurses (trae todas)
MockAPI -> App: [nurses]

App -> App: .find() local por usuario + password

alt Credenciales incorrectas
  App -> Nurse: Muestra error "Usuario o contraseña incorrectos"
else Credenciales correctas
  App -> App: Genera token mock

  alt Recordarme = true
    App -> Storage: setItem('@dietas:auth', JSON.stringify({token, user}))
  else Recordarme = false
    App -> App: No persiste, solo en RAM
  end

  App -> Nurse: Redirect a (app)/
end

== Logout ==
Nurse -> App: Toca "Cerrar sesion"
App -> Storage: removeItem('@dietas:auth')
App -> App: Limpia Zustand (user=null, token=null)
App -> Nurse: Redirect a /login

@enduml
